== Not GA - should be merged into existing pages ==
This should not be a Good Article and shouldn't even exist in its own right. The author(s) seems to have bulked up a relatively minor incident by providing a lot of background information that belongs on other existing pages in order to try to justify the existence of this article. The event simply isn't notable enough to justify its own page. Either the whole article should be moved onto the [[Tan Son Nhut Air Base]] or [[Republic of Vietnam Air Force]] page or it should be split up and dropped into the following pages: Background onto the Republic of Vietnam Air Force page; Prelude onto the [[Ho Chi Minh Campaign]] page; Attack on the Presidential Palace onto one of the Ho Chi Minh Campaign page or the [[Vietnam People's Air Force]] page or the [[Fall of Saigon]] page; Attack on Ton San Nhat onto one of the Vietnam People's Air Force page or the Fall of Saigon page or [[Operation Frequent Wind]] page or the Tan Son Nhat Airbase page; Aftermath split between Vietnam People's Air Force page and Republic of Vietnam Air Force page. Alternatively the Attack on Tan Son Nhat and aftermath section should be used to form a new article called Quyet Thang Squadron. [[User:Mztourist|Mztourist]] ([[User talk:Mztourist|talk]]) 09:14, 1 July 2011 (UTC)
